data.title: Homeward Bound
data.meta_description: Will you be home for the holidays?
data.text:
Will you be home for the holidays? On this day before Thanksgiving, you may be heading to your home or the home of family or friends. Whatâ€™s your favorite song about going home or being home? Share that below and we'll spin a set after 9am.

Here's what we played:

Imogen Heap "First Train Home"

Toots & The Maytals "Take Me Home, Country Roads"

Richard Shindell "Hazel's House"

Cornershop "Good to Be on the Road Back Home"

Edward Sharpe & The Magnetic Zeros "Home"
